Package vrpRep.utilities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DistanceCalculator
    Class used to implement and access distance calculator
    DistanceCalculatorEuc2D
    Calculate distance between two sets of euclidean 2D points.
    DistanceCalculatorEuc3D
    Calculate distance between two sets of euclidean 3D points.
    DistanceCalculatorGPS
    Calculate distance between two sets of latitude and longitude points
    DistanceCalculatorLink
    Returns the length of a link between two nodes
    DistanceCalculatorTest
    Test class to test various distance calculations.
    JDomParser
    This class implements a JDom parser
    XmlSchemaReader<T>
    Generic class used to read any xml file and store the data in a jaxb class structure (similar to DOM)
    The generic type T must point to jaxb class that represents head node of xml file
